title: Ten years gift problem
body:
Hey guys, I just get my riot kayle skin that is for ten years gift, but I think I didn't get the icon at the same time.
 Can some one show me what the summoner icon looks like?

replies.body: There are a lot of eligible accounts that need to be rewarded, so it's going to be a bit to receive everything.  Not every gift may be obtained at the same time.  We'll have updates on our[ support ticker.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-)  Hang tight!
You can see what the icon looks like [here](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/riot-games/announcements/thank-you).  The gifts are going out one by one and you should have them all by 9/23.
